# Live Trading Desk Orchestration - Instruction Map

This instruction map shows how to compose core_engine components into a real-time institutional trading desk with live market data, continuous risk monitoring, and automated execution capabilities.

## Live Trading Desk Component Stack

### Real-Time Brick Assembly
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│    HierarchicalSystemOrchestrator   │ ← System Control & Monitoring
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ LiveDataManager                     │ ← Real-Time Market Data
│ RegimeEngine (Real-Time)            │ ← Live Market Condition Analysis
│ StreamingIndicators                 │ ← Real-Time Signal Processing
│ AdaptiveFeatureEngine               │ ← Dynamic Feature Engineering
│ LiveSignalGenerator                 │ ← Real-Time Trading Signals
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ CentralRiskManager (Live)           │ ← Real-Time Risk Governance
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ StrategyManager (Live)              │ ← Active Strategy Management
│ RealTimeTradingEngine               │ ← Live Execution Planning
│ UnifiedExecutionEngine              │ ← Live Order Execution
